text: Canteen in the middle of an industrial area- chanced upon this stall that’s open on a Saturday. Taste wise it’s about 4 stars quite a regular lor mee. But I gave another star for the portion size it is HUGE for just $4. Friendly couple managing the store as well with a lot of regular customers.

Decent affordable noodles. Nothing much to complain about. Nothing outstanding but nothing bad about it either. Would say it's slightly above average in taste.
Friendly owner.
Reasonable prices, friendly owners and yummy noodles. Nothing to complain about.
Best fishball minced meat noodles! They were previously at Toh Guan 285A coffee shop and have now shifted here.
Ok food at a very affordable price.
